  "body": "When you rerender with two similar views that both contain an input (regardless of type), defaultValue is not evaluated.  This only happens when the element tree structure is the same/similar up to the input -- even if the inputs are two different types.\n\nYou can see it in this simple example where the new and old views are inputs inside a div:\nhttps://jsfiddle.net/u9rd10ab/\n",
